rcy for ever:","searchKeywords":["him","who","divided","the","red","sea","into","parts","for","his","mercy","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_14","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":14,"text":"and brought Israel through the midst of it: for his mercy for ever:","searchKeywords":["and","brought","israel","through","the","midst","for","his","mercy","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_15","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":15,"text":"and overthrew Pharao and his host in the Red Sea: for his mercy endures for ever.","searchKeywords":["and","overthrew","pharao","his","host","the","red","sea","for","mercy","endures","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_16","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":16,"text":"To him who led his people through the wilderness: for his mercy for ever.","searchKeywords":["him","who","led","his","people","through","the","wilderness","for","mercy","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_17","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":17,"text":"To him who smote great kings: for his mercy for ever:","searchKeywords":["him","who","smote","great","kings","for","his","mercy","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_18","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":18,"text":"and slew mighty kings; for his mercy for ever:","searchKeywords":["and","slew","mighty","kings","for","his","mercy","ever"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_135_19","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":135,"verse":19,"text":"Seon king of the Amorites: for his mercy for ever:","searchKeywords":["seon",